# Local Context First

Prioritizes local context and file-specific information over global patterns.

## Features

- Contextual relevance scoring
- Nearest-file analysis
- Dependency graph integration
- Semantic proximity detection

## Implementation

The system prioritizes:
1. Same file > directly imported files > project files > framework
2. Recent modifications > unchanged code
3. Explicit patterns > inferred patterns
4. Local conventions > global best practices

## Usage

Local context prioritization improves:
- Code completion accuracy
- Error detection relevance
- Suggestion quality
- Documentation generation 